scp -r root@116.196.113.163:/home/wwwroot/default/wordpress/wp-content/themes/blog-inn /root/桌面

上传blog-inn主题到服务器
scp -r /root/桌面/blog-inn root@116.196.113.163:/home/wwwroot/default/wordpress/wp-content/themes/
